---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { RoundtableTree } from "../components/RoundtableTree";
import { ROUNDTABLE } from "../lib/personas";
import { u } from "../lib/site";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Roundtable"
  description="Four personas, two rounds, one product question. The v1 product was killed and rebuilt by the cross-examination."
  wave="roundtable"
>
  <main class="roundtable">
    <div class="tracked">Wave 2 · The Roundtable</div>
    <h1 style="margin-top:0.75rem;">Four personas, two rounds, one product question.</h1>
    <p style="max-width:65ch;color:var(--ink-sub);margin-top:1rem;">
      <em>Topic.</em> {ROUNDTABLE.topic} The orchestrator selected four lenses with the largest expected disagreement on this question, ran an opening round, then forced each persona to address one other persona's R1 take in a second round &mdash; either to dismantle it, steelman it, or move toward it.
    </p>
    <p style="max-width:65ch;color:var(--ink-sub);margin-top:1rem;">
      Of all the agents in this session, the four roundtable personas (and their R2 doubles) are the only ones that loaded the full persona-skill profile rather than a prompt-level primer. <a href={u("/agents")}>How that worked.</a>
    </p>

    <RoundtableTree client:load />
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
